title: Woman Medium Skin Tone Bald
description: A woman with a medium skin tone and no hair. This emoji can represent a variety of things, including cancer survivors, personal style, or simply a bald head.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the bald woman with a medium skin tone emoji presents a striking and confident profile, her head smooth and elegantly rendered with Apple's characteristic soft rounded edges. The realistic lighting accentuates the contours of her face, conveying a sense of serene strength and individuality. This emoji, unique to Apple's design, is often used to represent resilience, bold personal choices, or to celebrate a distinctive identity.
